net.sf.mmm.util.value.base

Class PojoPathPropertyAccessor<POJO,VALUE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mmm.util.value.base.PojoPathPropertyAccessor<POJO,VALUE>
  • Type Parameters:
    POJO - is the generic type of the Pojo to access.
    VALUE - is the generic type of the POJOs property to access.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeReadValueType<VALUE>, PropertyAccessor<POJO,VALUE>

    public class PojoPathPropertyAccessor<POJO,VALUE>
extends Object
implements PropertyAccessor<POJO,VALUE>, AttributeReadValueType<VALUE>
    This is an implementation of PropertyAccessor using PojoPathNavigator (based on reflection).
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
